  "Energy that is freely available from the sun": "",
  "Energy stored exclusively in chemical bonds": "",
  "The total kinetic energy of all molecules in a system": "",
  "The portion of a system's energy that is available to do work at constant temperature and pressure": "",
  "Gibbs free energy (G) measures the energy available to do work. A negative ΔG indicates a spontaneous (exergonic) reaction. A positive ΔG indicates a non-spontaneous (endergonic) reaction that requires energy input.": "",
