  "Constitutive enzyme expression regardless of energy status, particularly in the context of energy": "",
  "Positive feedback amplification, since standard models of energy behavior predict this outcome under normal conditions": "",
  "Cells regulate ATP production through feedback mechanisms. Key catabolic enzymes (like PFK in glycolysis) are allosterically inhibited by ATP (high energy signal) and activated by AMP/ADP (low energy signal), maintaining a balance between energy supply and demand.": "",
  "An environmental scientist compares the energy efficiency of a food chain: plants capture 1% of solar energy, herbivores convert 10% of plant energy, and carnivores convert 10% of herbivore energy. Based on thermodynamic principles, why is energy lost at each trophic level?": "",
